{"tid":189124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當值時搣女下屬臉部兼捽耳珠　警署警長普通襲擊罪成","createTime":"2017-04-06T08:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T08:28:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c9b650f5036351fb59afa108000fa6dbd42cef0","tid":189124,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170406/large/1491465445_0468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170406%2Flarge%2F1491465445_0468.jpg&h=24ffde02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告蔡德祥(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n男警署警長被指當值時搣女下屬臉部及捽其耳珠，並拍打女下屬臀部，被控普通襲擊及非禮共4罪。案件經審訊後，警長今被裁定三項普通襲擊罪成，他獲准保釋至本月19日判刑，期間取得其背景及感化報告。<br />\n<br />\n明年將退休並預料長俸達200萬的被告蔡德祥（53歲），曾於自辯時承認曾對事主搣臉、手臂及搣耳珠，但強調均沒有惡意，只是抱著嬉戲的心態。警長亦承認曾拍事主背腰一下，用意是提醒對方要坐直，並沒有猥褻或攻擊意圖。"},{"pid":"3f318757b2acd63f6953e04e23c0bd2f4d406aeb","tid":189124,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:09:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56529166&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56529166%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170406&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=955a4259\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56529166%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170406&h=1282e6ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56529166&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170406</a>"},{"pid":"ad42dd84bd5400939b5248194bfd67d1c0ccfd82","tid":189124,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"非禮呢？"},{"pid":"fbcc486c47496f65c0069d5b12dd81601749edd5","tid":189124,"uid":20933,